Keen!

479
00:26:44.920 --> 00:26:47.890
<i>♪ So happy together ♪</i>

480
00:26:58.600 --> 00:27:01.285
Ah. it's gonna be okay.

481
00:27:01.480 --> 00:27:02.845
It's gonna be okay.

482
